channel.title: AFGscape 2007 - Brining back the old memories [RELEASE]
channel.description:
So here it is, after a while working on this i'm releasing again a great server ;) Why? Because i couln't find a good vps to host it on. Had around 6-10 players in 2 days when i hosted it on my own computer. Btw you need to use eclipse to rune the server.
